Windows Project Files

---------------------------



1) General Steps



   a) open the project file according to your development environment

   b) set BOOST & CPPUNIT includes in either Tools->Options->Project&Solutions->VC++ Directories->Include Files-> OR pdfedit->Property Pages->C/C++->General->Additional Include Directories

   c) set debug parameters pdfedit->Property Pages->Configuration Properties->Debugging->Command Arguments to e.g. "-all -dir ..\testset -files ..\doc\zadani.pdf" 

   d) build solution

   e) run tests 



Tested:

VC 2005 Express Edition

	-> Debug version

